{"tid":2434594,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有限創意●雷驚天地龍蛇蟄 - 余家強","createTime":"2021-03-05T15:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T15:44:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19ac7b2261b78f8c2f46ce146b0a68d7f9438425","tid":2434594,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210305/J35LEEFUIREZRN6IGEIQTT3EFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210305%2FJ35LEEFUIREZRN6IGEIQTT3EFI%2F&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=9d7ac44f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210305%2FJ35LEEFUIREZRN6IGEIQTT3EFI%2F&h=57a1bc3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210305/J35LEEFUIREZRN6IGEIQTT3EFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n有限創意●雷驚天地龍蛇蟄 - 余家強<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rc5cvymsMytx8CKvLGbs009RNMk=/1800x936/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RAR2FQLSIRB4JF454EPNLWX2YU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRc5cvymsMytx8CKvLGbs009RNMk%3D%2F1800x936%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRAR2FQLSIRB4JF454EPNLWX2YU.png&h=e58f9c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天3月5日，廿四節氣屬驚蟄（音疾）。宋朝黃庭堅有首詩〈清明〉說：<br />\n<br />\n「佳節清明桃李笑，野。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題目叫〈清明〉，「雷。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n古人看得化，清明花。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃庭堅詩愛用典故，此首倒用得。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「士甘焚死不公侯」出自春。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃庭堅將兩件事擺在一起，含心思。小人得志，君子失意。當權者往往重賞無才無德鼠輩，貪其擦鞋奉承，容易控制。你看某助理教授高薪厚職，兼疑用長者八達通，而竟執教政治與行政學系，難怪香港政風焉能不腐敗？反觀，被捕議員如譚文豪，連飛機師工作也掉了，轉行開茶餐廳，放下身段，不亢不卑，跟「乞祭餘」的「妾婦」格調霄壤雲泥。當權者親小人遠君子，千古定律。<br />\n<br />\n龍蛇之間，應該如何抉擇？詩末感慨「滿眼蓬蒿共一丘」，看似消極，卻想深一層，既然錢財勝敗轉頭空，做人，還是頂天立地的好。黃庭堅硬把驚蟄寫進〈清明〉，我猜，乃要伸張正義。今天去鵝頸橋，不為私怨，原為公憤，祝禱魔消道長，揚善除惡。<br />\n<br />\n打小人，祭。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n電郵：yuekakeung@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n逢星期五刊登"}]}